      <p class="text-2xl font-semibold font-montserrat">100% free.</p>
      <p class="">We believe that everyone has the right to exercise and, by extension, to the 
        best tools available, so carnage and all its features are and will remain completely free of charge. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-200 p-4 rounded-xl">
      <p class="text-2xl font-semibold font-montserrat text-justify">Feature-rich.</p>
      <p class="">Carnage is feature rich, allowing you to customize your workouts exactly to
        your needs. Never worry about having to write down your workouts on spreadsheets ever
        again! </p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-200 p-4 rounded-xl">
      <p class="text-2xl font-semibold font-montserrat text-justify">Up to date.</p>
      <p class="">Unlike most workout trackers, we stay up to date with the current literature to
        ensure the best possible service for all our users. No more 4 sets of 12 reps.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
